  fhir:text [
     fhir:status [ fhir:v "generated" ] ;
     fhir:div [ fhir:v "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Narrativa gerada: ImplementationGuide heartland.fhir.us.protocol</b></p><a name=\"heartland.fhir.us.protocol\"> </a><a name=\"hcheartland.fhir.us.protocol\"> </a><h2>HeartlandProtocolIG</h2><p>O URL oficial para este guia de implementação é: </p><pre>https://fhir.heartlandprotocol.org/ImplementationGuide/heartland.fhir.us.protocol</pre><div><p>FHIR R4 Implementation Guide for the HEARTLAND Protocol v3.2 — a clinical implementation toolkit for primary care-led heart failure management in rural and resource-limited US settings. Defines profiles, extensions, questionnaires, and value sets enabling EHR vendors to exchange HEARTLAND-structured data (risk assessments, care plans, remote monitoring observations).</p>\n</div></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
