       fhir:description [ fhir:v "Responses to the HeartlandRiskInputQuestionnaire for PatientExampleRural. Six items answered true (age >=75, prior HF hosp 6mo, SBP <100, CKM Stage 3-4, distance >50 mi, limited social support) totaling 11 points -> High Risk tier. Referenced by RiskAssessmentExampleHigh.basis[0]." ] ;
