       fhir:name [ fhir:v "HEARTLAND Facility Implementation Tier" ] ;
       fhir:description [ fhir:v "Identifies the HEARTLAND Protocol v3.2 implementation tier (1 Minimal, 2 Standard, 3 Advanced) at which a facility, organization, or care plan operates. Drives which protocol activities (monitoring, GDMT cadence, education, follow-up) are operationally feasible." ] ;
